		<section id="case__x" class="result result__intro">
		  <h1>What is this?</h1>
		  <p>This site is meant as a quick reference guide for using two drugs at a time. Additional research must be done before using or combining any drugs. I'm not responsible if you use this and bad things happen.</p>
		  <p>This site used data from and was influenced by a <a href="http://wiki.tripsit.me/wiki/Drug_combinations">difficult to read drug combination chart</a> from TripSit.com.</p>
		</section>

		<!-- Same input -->
		<section id="case__0" class="result result__same">
		  <h1 class="emoji">😸</h1>
		  <h1>Have fun</h1>
